data.description: Wonderful country home on 9 acres with pond and woods. Home sits isolated from view of the road. The home has four bedrooms, and two full baths with a nursery just off the main bedroom. The rest of the house is an open floor plan format. There is a wood burning stove in the family room. The stocked pond just off the large front porch is ideal for enjoying evenings watching the kids fish. Theabove ground pool has been removed. There are fruit trees and a large garden should you want to continue it. The property also has a large pole barn that would make a great shop, or place to store vehicles. Home now has high speed fiber internet for those that want to work from home. Property sits 5 minutes from Hawesville.
